{"tid":2088973,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[激勵] 飛越瘋人院 Once flew over cuckoo's nest","createTime":"2020-07-01T12:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T03:44:30.000Z","uid":340796,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f843c1cc2aa5cc05a355fbb7bfc890f76827b0e8","tid":2088973,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:31:31.000Z","msg":"男主角McMurphy 因罪被判入精神病院<br />\n佢嘅出現為病人死板枯燥的生活帶來衝擊，<br />\n更在院中散播反叛的種子<br />\n自此病人係院中開始會對護士長表達相反意見，<br />\n並對無理要求提出反抗<br />\n<br />\n故事經歷反抗、壓迫甚至以死相練，發展到最後男主角被迫食藥，令佢喪失獨立思考能力<br />\n自此以後不再是當初的McMurphy<br />\n<br />\n酋長不甘男主角被奪去可貴的靈魂<br />\n忍痛了斷佢嘅生命<br />\n佢一直保持沉默，但沒有忘記男主角的熱情如何激起心中壓抑已久的火炬<br />\n呢個意識形態埋藏在心中，等候一個適當的時機承繼男主角當初的宏願<br />\n佢窮盡一切力量抬起200噸重的雲石水台<br />\n砸破窗口，離開瘋人院，向著黎明奔去<br />\n<br />\n以上為電影內容分享，非常值得一睇<br />\n睇到最後哭能咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />酋長<br />\n<br />\n有冇睇過戲同原著的巴絲分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a8194ac6b6e038873e45427407e342dbc988ff","tid":2088973,"uid":124439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:33:52.000Z","msg":"什麼是自由<br />\n自由就是看不見但內心感受到<br />\n推薦月黑高飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a549ad714adbd89fb5c17e84dfe204b82b2a969","tid":2088973,"uid":250639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:35:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0073486/reviews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imdb.com%2Ftitle%2Ftt0073486%2Freviews&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=0fc670f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0073486/reviews</a>"},{"pid":"5a42b20f7c8fb56bd44a65059186386572832e5e","tid":2088973,"uid":250639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35a8194ac6b6e038873e45427407e342dbc9